{"about_the_game":"<i>OscarWildeCard</i> is a fast paced card battler that is easy to learn but has surprising depth.<br><br><i>&quot;one of my favourite short games of the year&quot; - Gay Time's Best And Queerest Video Games of 2023</i><br><br><i>Top 5 Game in the Queer Games Bundle 2023 - Gamecity Hamburg</i><br><br><i>&quot;hilarious&quot; - jimjimmyjimjim</i><br><br>A new life awaits you in The Golden Palace, the world's most exclusive apartment building.<br><br>But standing in the way of social success is Oscar Wildecard, the witty but cruel socialite.<br><br>To progress to the top of the building and victory you must co-host a series of dinner parties. Battle by inviting the best guests to your side of the table, each represented by a card.<br><br>Guests have strengths and weaknesses depending on who they are and with whom they sit!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892840/extras/OWC_gifs_cupid.gif?t=1717049219\" /><br><br>Defend, attack, or throw the rules of the game out the window with special Wildecards. The choices are yours. Just remember, always forgive your enemies, nothing will annoy them more.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Story mode with 15 levels and an estimated 90 minutes of play.<br></li><li>Conquest mode -- play a series of challenge quests with special rules.<br></li><li>Hilarious and handsome images by comic-book artist Joe Phillips.<br></li><li>No in-app purchases. All cards are unlocked as you play.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892840/extras/OWC_gifs_electric.gif?t=1717049219\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717049219","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892840/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1717049219","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i